OL,4,CLorry driver shortage threatens Haribo
OL,5,Csweets
OL,6, German confectionery giant Haribo has
OL,7, said it is struggling to deliver its
OL,8, sweets to shops in the UK because of a
OL,9, shortage of lorry drivers.
OL,11,FA spokesperson said that like many
OL,12,Fother manufacturers and retailers, it
OL,13,Fwas "experiencing challenges" that were
OL,14,Fhampering supplies.
OL,16,FThe problems affect all Haribo sweets,
OL,17,Fincluding Goldbears and Tangfastics.
OL,19,FThe haulage industry has blamed the
OL,20,Fpandemic and Brexit for thousands of
OL,21,Funfilled HGV driver jobs.
